{
  "texts": [
    "In this scenario we hope to explore what the potential of GPT models is with respect to handling gender phenomena across languages.",
    "We ought to note that the tags (<F>, <M> and <A>) with which sentences are annotated in the gENder-IT challenge set were removed from the English sentences for the prompt.",
    "For convenience, we added the tags to the examples provided in the subsequent section.",
    "We conducted a manual analysis/evaluation of the translations generated by ChatGPT for both scenarios.",
    "For Scenario 1, the one where the prompt did not explicitly state that alternatives are to be generated, only 5 out of the 50 sentences did not miss valid alternatives in terms of gender."
  ]
}